results.title: Double Cross
results.description: Mr. Jip switches Dazzler and Diamondback's bodies, and the X-Men have to gather four mystic objects so he will change them back; Diamondback (back in her old body) steals the pieces for Llyra and Ghaur.

results.title: Jubilation Day
results.description: Jubilee follows the X-Men from the mall to the Australian Outback where she secretly makes a home in their new hideout.

results.title: The Saga of the Serpent Crown Part 3: Serpent In the Garden
You Must Remember This
results.description: Maybe not the MOST convoluted and confusing X-Men story ever, but it comes close.

results.title: Kings of Pain Part 3: Queens of Sacrifice
results.description: The X-Men, X-Force and New Warriors fail to keep Piecemeal from merging with Proteus.

results.title: The Razor's Edge Part 2: The Killing Stroke
The Origin of the X-Men
results.description: Mojo reviews the origins and history of the X-Men.

results.title: The Enemy Within
results.description: Wolverine battles his adamantium skeleton.

results.title: A Fire In the Sky!
results.description: The X-Men battle Arkon and are transported to his world where they are asked to help save it.

results.title: Nightcrawler's Inferno
results.description: Full origin of Nightcrawler; The X-Men and Doc Strange try to rescue Kurt from his foster mother's hell; Amanda Sefton is Kurt's long lost love Jimaine.

results.title: Ou, La La--Badoon!
results.description: The X-Men and the Invisible Girl travel to Arkon's world to save the rest of the FF (who have been captured) and free Arkon's people from a Badoon invasion.

results.title: Blood Feud!
results.description: Dracula demands Storm's aid in obtaining the Darkhold so no one else will have the power to banish him, but a dark and sinister Kitty intervenes.

results.title: Scavenger Hunt
results.description: Impossible Man steals X-Mansion during an X-Men baseball game and the scavenger hunt fun begins; The X-Men chase Impy to the Shield Helicarrier (where he absconds with Fury's eye patch), the Savage Land (where Zabu is the target), Avenger's Mansion (to make off with the Wasp's wardrobe), and to the offices of Marvel Comics (where he tries to steal Stan Lee).

results.title: The Adventures of Lockheed the Space Dragon and His Pet Girl, Kitty
results.description: Illyana's fairy tale.

results.title: And Men Shall Call Him Warlock
Cover #19889
results.description: If Dr. Strange kills Shuma-Gorath, the Ancient One dies

results.title: Finally, Shuma-Gorath!
results.description: Strange enters Ancient One's mind, and battles Shuma-Gorath for mankind's Soul. To destroy Shuma-Gorath, who feeds on mind of A.O., Strange kills the Ancient One!  A.O. becomes One with the Universe.

results.title: Cover #19891
results.description: Baron Mordo has imprisoned soul of Dr. Strange

results.title: Homecoming!
results.description: Strange goes to home of Ancient One, & tells Hamir the Hermit about the how he killed Ancient One to destroy Shuma-Gorath, and of A.O.'s rebirth as One with Universe. Strange is now Sorcerer Supreme.

results.title: The Origin of Dr. Strange
results.description: Origin of Dr. Strange (reprint)

results.title: The Many Traps of Baron Mordo
results.description: Mordo traps Strange in an enchanted cylinder.  Strange escapes by traveling down through the Earth, and poses as Ancient One to thwart Mordo's attack.

results.title: No man walks twice thru the Doorway of Doom!
Portal to the Past!
results.description: Strange chooses Clea to be his disciple. He goes to make peace with Baron Mordo, and is entranced by Gypsy Queen, from whom Mordo stole the Book of Cagliostro. Strange follow Mordo into past.

results.title: Time Doom
results.description: Strange follows Mordo to 18th c. Paris to confront Cagliostro, who is revealed as Sise-Neg, magician from 30th c. Sise-Neg is traveling back through time, controlling mystical energy to become God!

results.title: Sise-Neg Genesis
results.description: Sise-Neg journeys back to dawn of Creation, absorbing all mystical power. Mordo schemes to be disciple. Strange implores Sise-Neg not to abandon mankind. Sise-Neg becomes Genesis & recreates universe.

results.title: There's a Mountain On Sunset Boulevard!
While the World Spins Mad
results.description: Strange is hit by truck, and enters unreal dream world of Nightmare.  Nightmare is in league with nameless powerful other, warns Strange that he shall learn who, and the answer will bring him Death!

results.title: Hey, Ma!  They're Blitzin' the Bronx!
